    "description": "Are you a skilled Consultant Physician looking for your next big career move? Piramal Pharma in Bhopal offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Piramal Pharma:\nPiramal Pharma is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Piramal Pharma!",
